The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Colombo to host all ties

New Delhi: The BCCI has agreed to SLCs request that all matches of next months tri-series be played in Colombo. The meet, featuring South Africa as third team, was originally scheduled in Colombo and Dambulla 

All matches would be held in Colombo, confirmed BCCI secretary Niranjan Shah. (PTI) 




